headline: Crunch Franchise Brings State-of-the-Art Crunch 3.0 Gym to San Antonio, Texas
summary: Crunch Fitness today announced the upcoming opening of Crunch San Antonio Thousand Oaks in San Antonio, Texas. The $5 million, 35,000-square-foot state-of-the-art fitness facility will open its doors in Summer 2026. Operated by Crunch Fitness franchisee The Undefeated Tribe, Crunch San Antonio Thousand Oaks will be located at 4319 Thousand Oaks Drive, next to Walmart, creating a new fitness offering for residents of San Antonio.
